                    <li>‚Ä¢ Our team will contact you within 24 hours</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ We'll schedule a detailed consultation call</li>
                    <li>‚Ä¢ Project timeline and deliverables will be discussed</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <div className="flex gap-4 justify-center">
                  <Button onClick={() => window.location.href = '/'}>
                    Return to Home
